


Installation of MongoDB 

www.mongodb.com     ->    Products   ->       community Server   ->     On-Premises       ->    Download and install   

link to download     ->           https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/enterprise

To change mongoDB Startup from Automatic  to manual   ->  open Services app in windows   -  select  mongoDB    -  open its Properties  - set Startup to maual 


install compass from tools  to run MongoDB in GUI   ->  https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/compass

install shell from tools to run MongoDB in CLI   and extract it into  mongoDB folder   ->    https://www.mongodb.com/try/download/shell    
